      "content": "hey so im about 5 months pregnant and i have this insane sinus infection that just wont go away. my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i was gonna grab some Sudafed but i wasnt sure if that was okay? or maybe i should just take some cipro to knock it out fast? what do u think?",
